Class ClientHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.ClientHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, java.rmi.Remote, ViewListener

    public class ClientHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements ViewListener, java.lang.Runnable
    This is the Visitor (Visitor Pattern) used to decode the messages received by a client (only for Socket purpose)
